</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><emphasis>Returns</emphasis>&#160;:</term><listitem><simpara> A pointer to the new <link linkend="GimpFileEntry"><type>GimpFileEntry</type></link> widget.
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist></refsect2>
